{"tid":403432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3人撕中大民主牆港獨單張　操英語女子坐車離開　司機高呼「英國走狗」","createTime":"2017-09-17T07:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T05:36:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"91676a6702831b201ca803f050ab3ee3851b40c1","tid":403432,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/908edfd0dd412145ecbfe6adc6271b6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F908edfd0dd412145ecbfe6adc6271b6f.jpg&h=9f0105c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學校長沈祖堯日前公開要求學生會盡快移除與「港獨」的宣傳品，否則校方會主動移除。記者今午約1時巡視民主牆，未見有新標語，另文化廣場的橫額亦未被移走，惟下午約1時20分，先後有3名人士撕下民主牆上印有「拒絕沉淪，唯有獨立」的單張。<br />\n<br />\n首先撕走紙張的為一操普通話男士，他未有回應是否中大學生或學生職員。被問為何撕走單張及是否不同意當中內容，該男士表示「我同意呀，所以才撕掉」。<br />\n而另一位撕走單張的男士，記者表明身分上前詢問原因，該男士回應「我見有人撕走」，又指自己是「公眾人士」，因不贊成單張內容而撕走。問及擅自撕走民主牆上單張可能違法，該男士指「他們（張貼標語者）也犯法」，又說不介意目擊者報警。<br />\n<br />\n隨後一名白衣女士突然大幅度撕走民主牆上的標語，正在當值的學生會外務秘書李文耀即上前阻止並詢問身分，該女士未有回應，其後乘坐私人座駕離開。約2分鐘後，其座駕駛回現場，司機開窗並大叫「英國走狗」。<br />\n李文耀批評撕走標語者行為，「不文明及野蠻的行為，若不滿可向學生會反映，而不是擅自撕走」。他指事出突然，將與其他幹事商討跟進方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505628794557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505628794557&d=9ulIGd%2B19GD%2FoCX6EKh8FzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=79b7a8a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F1505628794557&h=0710117f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170917/s00001/1505628794557</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/9041cac8cc2173a19a5ccfcece20b3b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F9041cac8cc2173a19a5ccfcece20b3b1.jpg&h=d6925d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170917/s00001/90a916a5cff8b4a00693a00b0ac14db4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170917%2Fs00001%2F90a916a5cff8b4a00693a00b0ac14db4.jpg&h=278fee68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d2e2c73c62b2b3125f3a9deae667b68f5016ec4","tid":403432,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文化廣場再有不明人士搗亂，請同學盡快支援！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8d2cd77e9c81e367180756c0511b33f99bb5356e","tid":403432,"uid":61678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"走住黎屌 冇撚用"},{"pid":"e896ae8a234f6c12a787957c963f1dbdaddc6e36","tid":403432,"uid":41821,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"你撕左我咪貼返上去lo,<br />\n我唔撚信佢咁撚得閒日日去撕"},{"pid":"387834820e4a6bc8c07197e04fa7d172c76a1d50","tid":403432,"uid":122745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"小學雞動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07cfa061d622aab44c5fb3493e938c5a30ab6eec","tid":403432,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ddd5806a74c2e742353e56b4d250e409182915b","tid":403432,"uid":69971,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fec46827c29c042635b348657893d4bfc698ec","tid":403432,"uid":38666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"你斯左未貼番囉 冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbb73b604903c06d3ae2210f407d152bf5b25d7","tid":403432,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0